<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/euforic/nar/ib3_gb.htm 193.128.6.150 19970222020425 text/html 9745
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 02:04:11 GMT
