t.</i> </ul><p><hr width=71%><p><h3>The WORLD in Your Kitchen<p>by Troth Wells</h3>This offers:<p><ul><li>Attractive design and easy step-by step cooking methods <li>A profusion of full-page colour photos of people preparing, cooking and eating their meals<li>More than 150 delicious vegetarian recipes from around the world<li>A full nutrition guide<li>Vegetarianism set in the context of today's factory-farm world </ul><p><i>'For anyone who wants to cook with more vegetables and less meat but isn't sure how or why, Troth Wells has given us The Joy of Cooking for vegetarians.'</i><p><ul> Joanne Kates, Toronto Globe and Mail. </ul><p><hr width=71%><p><img align=right hspace=10 vspace=10 border=1 src="ni_pix/ni_books.gif"><a name="ordering"><h3>TO ORDER</h3> Please send your name and address with payment to the appropriate address below. If you are not happy  just send it back within 14 days and we will refund your money.<p><b>AOTEAROA/NEW ZEALAND</b><br>New Internationalist<br>PO Box 4499<br>Christchurch<br>Phone and fax: (03) 3656-153<p>Single book price $25 plus $3 p&p Total <b>$28 </b><br>Special offer for both books $40 plus $5 Total<b>$45 </b><p><b>AUSTRALIA</b><br>New Internationalist<br>7 Hutt Street<br>Adelaide 5000.<br>Phone: (08) 232 1563<br>Fax: (08) 232 1887<p>Single book price $26.50 plus $7 p&p Total <b>$33.50</b> <br>Special offer for both books $43 plus $8 Total <b>$51.00 </b><p><b>CANADA</b><br>New Internationalist<br>35 Riviera Drive, No 17<br>Markham, ON<br>L3R 8N4<br>Phone: (416) 588 6478<br>Fax (416) 537 6435 [GST reg no R121784854] <p>Single book price $16.95 plus $3 p/h plus $1.40 GST Total <b> $21.35</b><br>Special offer for both books $28.95 plus $4 p/h plus $2.30 GST Total <b>$35.25</b><p><b>UNITED KINGDOM</b><br>New Internationalist<br>55 Rectory Road<br>Oxford<br>OX4 1BW<br>Phone: (01865) 728181<br>Fax:	(01865) 793152<p>Single bo