<H1><B>THE LAND IS OURS</B></H1>



<H3><I>a landrights campaign for Britain</I></H3>



TLIO

</CENTER>



<CENTER>

<H2>

[TLIO]

LAND ESSAYS 2[TLIO]

<br>

<i>4.  Land Tax</i>

</H2>



</CENTER>







<table width=600 border=0 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=1>



<TR>

<TD BGCOLOR="#008080" ALIGN=LEFT>



<a name="contents"></a>[TLIO]<B><Font Size=+2>C</Font>ONTENTS</B>(click any row of trees to return here)

</TD>

</TR>





<TR>

<TD>

<A href="#shirlyh">DOT Braveheart</a>, Shirly-Anne Hardy

<br>

<a href="#johns">DOTBeating Back the Bandits</a>, John Seymour

<br>

<a href="#ronaldb">DOTAn Open Letter to Tony Blair</a>, Ronald Banks

<p>

</td>

</tr>





<tr>

