<h1><center>"THE INTERNET - THAT'S ALL I NEED"</center></h1>
<br clear=left><br>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<b><font size=+1>The last thing any overworked teacher wants is more paperwork.</font><p></b>

So here's an amusing little video instead:<p>

<p>


It tells you how to find materials - in a simple-to-retrieve format - that you need to teach important global issues.<p>

<ul><li>Cut down your lesson preparation time.<p>

<li>Stop wasting hours wandering in cyberspace.<p>

<li>Sort out the difference between e-mail and the internet....<p></ul>


<b>So what are you waiting for?<p>

The video costs £9.25 (UK) or £11.25 (outside UK).  This price includes post and package.<p>


To order your copy send your name, address, which school you teach at and a cheque made out to the OneWorld Broadcasting Trust to:<p>

One World Broadcasting Trust<br>
