<DOCNO>WT17-B16-75</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA008-000080-B035-226</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ecdpm.org:80/ni/issue275/editor.html 193.128.6.150 19970222082433 text/html 4055
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 08:24:13 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Fri, 09 Feb 1996 13:44:22 GMT
